Jacqueline Beer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacqueline_Beer 0 Jacqueline Beer (born Jacqueline Vangramberg; 14 October 1932 in Paris, France), sometimes credited as Jacqueline Baer, is a former Hollywood film and television actress who was Miss France in the 1954 Miss Universe Pageant. She is Chair of the Board of Directors of the Thor Heyerdahl Institute, located in Larvik, Norway, birthplace of her last husband, scientist Thor Heyerdahl.
